title: About
text:
We are a group of four students of Sciences Po Paris, currently in our first year of Master of Research in Economics.
This website aims to present in an extended way our work for our class of Microeconomics 2.

title: Microeconomics 2 project website
text:
Hello there, this is the website of the Microeconomics project of Chambon Lionel, Gugelmo Cavalheiro Dias Paulo, Pavlovich Karina, and Soufflet Morgane !
We are doing our project about a Game Theoretical approach of pollution taxation.
